{"tid":1992561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日郭嘉全打電話上晴朗解說！","createTime":"2020-04-28T08:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T08:46:18.000Z","uid":254383,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2fcc6bc3daea380f01847309d1032b9b5ba65920","tid":1992561,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:25:19.000Z","msg":"警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉全以為自己好打得，同「晴朗的一天出發」主持講太古城中心行動。<br />\n<br />\n主持：明明一個人冇犯禁聚令，點解當日警員話湊夠數就拉得人？<br />\n郭：呢個係新條例，我哋會向警員講執法準則，每個行動後會檢討。<br />\n<br />\n主持：即前線有冇濫用法例？<br />\n郭：好難就一個同事理解。<br />\n<br />\n主持：咁你個人點睇 ？<br />\n郭：佢講呢句說話，我好難武斷話啱唔啱。<br />\n<br />\n主持：會問那位警員嗎？<br />\n郭：我們每次見到會檢討，要自強不息。<br />\n<br />\n主持：會檢討這個案嗎？<br />\n郭：每次行動都會檢討。<br />\n<br />\n主持：檢討完未？有冇結果？<br />\n郭：這個很難答，每次都會檢討，希望每次做得更好。<br />\n<br />\n主持：你哋話過警員不應叫市民曱甴，當日太古城仍有市民被叫曱甴。<br />\n郭：點都好啦，我哋會提返同事，確保同事有同理心，點都好啦，我同記者有交往，佢地話我哋同事的工作有改善，做得好咗。<br />\n<br />\n主持：點解警員嘲諷趙家賢耳仔？<br />\n鄭姓指揮官：趙家賢已向平機會投訴，我不便作出任何評論。<br />\n<br />\n主持：上次平機會查警員展示記者身分證時，你哋都有承認唔啱。<br />\n鄭：有唔同，上次可以做得好一點，今次警員點解擺隻手去耳仔要特別理解。<br />\n<br />\n主持：咁有冇問返原因？<br />\n鄭：我哋仲問緊現場同事，如果趙議員感到受屈，可以同我哋聯絡返。<br />\n<br />\n主持：鄭sir，你當日也在現場。<br />\n鄭：現場好嘈雜，好多謾罵聲，同事隻手擺耳仔是否聽唔到？我不能代佢答。 <br />\n<br />\n主持：似乎你哋有100萬個藉口比犯錯警員，對示威者就唔會放過，係咪對警員犯錯太寬容？<br />\n鄭：唔可以咁講，警察面對好多挑戰和困難，我哋遇到查詢都會跟進，希望更加專業。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解咁鐘意自殺式PR <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f4682e2fb0854787e457a9ca8c1dd51ff020ab","tid":1992561,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715611555/posts/10156850578141556/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715611555%2Fposts%2F10156850578141556%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPmo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=c5151df8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715611555/posts/10156850578141556/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"6bf8917ef4538b56406c8dadfcf3da883d66013d","tid":1992561,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"自認比記者讚做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38ededac0b3e376d243b9788da736cbf6b7f03b","tid":1992561,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:30:07.000Z","msg":"個病都就完 仲解釋緊條法例？ 如果警察唔清楚條法例點執行仲點可以去執法？"},{"pid":"03e01e64c88362fc6706f3443e905d09d6b99c5d","tid":1992561,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bf8917ef4538b56406c8dadfcf3da883d66013d","tid":1992561,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"自認比記者讚做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:31:36.000Z","msg":"文匯大公讚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3336ab7dca088ac74265552c4e911e51499b94","tid":1992561,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03e01e64c88362fc6706f3443e905d09d6b99c5d","tid":1992561,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bf8917ef4538b56406c8dadfcf3da883d66013d","tid":1992561,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"自認比記者讚做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:31:36.000Z","msg":"文匯大公讚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:32:30.000Z","msg":"前面班黑警黑記黑記咁叫人 仲棍打癲狗記者然後另轉身走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g